Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:12.72,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{That'd be me! Akina Chihiro.}Là tôi đây. Akina Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:15.16,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, Manager! Sorry about that.}Quản lý! Xin lỗi anh...
