Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:42.31,Main,Yamgishi (F),0,0,0,,{I'm in the arms of Tuesday, \Nwhile dreaming of the distant weekend...}Tao đang trong vòng tay của Thứ 3,\N mơ về ngày cuối tuần xa xăm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:45.44,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{It doesn't matter how you dress it up. \NIt's still only Tuesday.}Dù có nói gì thì hôm nay vẫn là thứ 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:50.20,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Stop being stupid and get to work.}Đừng nói nhảm nữa mà làm việc đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:54.83,Main,Yamgishi (M),0,0,0,,{Cool as ice, like always, Hayakawa-san.}Vẫn lạnh lùng như mọi khi, Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:59.10,Main,Yamgishi (M),0,0,0,,{Zakishino, this is gonna be a long week!}Zakishiro, tuần này lâu quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:01.85,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's the same length as it was last week.}Tuần nào chả như nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.85,0:01:04.21,Main,Yamagishi (M),0,0,0,,{I'm talking experientially, bro!}Tao đang nói về sự cảm nhận.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:05.87,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san!}Shinozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:06.71,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai?}Chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:08.96,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What do you want to do for lunch today?}Hôm nay buổi trưa em tính làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:12.16,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sorry, I made plans to eat with Yamagishi-kun.}Xin lỗi, em định đi ăn với Yamagishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:10.87,Italics - Top,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Such a cutie!}Dễ thương ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:13.21,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:15.78,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Next time, then!}Thế lần sau nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:19.22,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Step, step, step...}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:22.44,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I think I'm good with this being a long week.}Tao thích tuần nào cũng dài hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:24.50,Main,Yamagishi(M),0,0,0,,{Damn, man!}Mẹ mày!
