Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:02:59.39,Main - Top,Manager,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-kun!}Shinozaki nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:00.20,Main - Top,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yes, sir?!}Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.05,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Care to join me for lunch?}Đi ăn cùng anh không?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:06.20,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{The boss where I work...}Cấp trên của mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:09.22,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{is someone I truly don't understand.}là một người khó hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.71,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,Thế công việc như nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:16.96,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Thanks to Senpai's help, \Nit's been a lot of fun.}Nhờ có chị ấy giúp đỡ mà nó rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.60,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{That's good to hear.}Tốt quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:21.47,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{We have a hard time getting new personnel,}Bọn anh gặp khó khăn trong tuyển người mới,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:26.85,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{so when you were hired, Katase-san \Nwas so excited, she became a handful.}nên khi em vào công ty, Katase đã\N rất háo hức tới mức phiền luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:28.28,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She was?}Vậy ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:29.35,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Indeed she was.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:32.35,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,Cứ như mới hôm qua vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.84,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{I'm thinking of interviewing this one.}Anh sẽ phỏng vấn cậu này.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:39.61,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Is it a boy or a girl?}Là trai hay gái ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.47,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{Interview's all done. \NHe seems nice, so it's a done deal.}Phỏng vấn xong rồi. Có vẻ ổn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:46.27,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{When's he coming? When are you expecting?}Khi nào cậu ấy vào làm? Lịch làm là như nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:49.87,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{At the time I wondered, \N"Huh? Am I having a baby?"}Ủa? Lúc đó mình cứ tưởng mình có con thì phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.10,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{My son.}Con trai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.40,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, who?}Hả? Ai ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:53.47,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Manager...}Quản lý...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:58.12,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Could you not tell Shinozaki-san \Nthese weird stories?}Anh đừng nói mấy chuyện kì cục cho em ấy được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.12,0:03:59.26,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai?}Chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:02.89,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Excuse me, could I get the tuna and \Nmushroom Arrabbiata, and the shrimp...}Xin lỗi, tôi muốn cá ngừ, nấm Arrabbiata và tôm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:05.05,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are you listening to me?!}Anh có nghe không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.64,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Why, of course I am.}Có nghe mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:09.60,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{She's cute when she's mad, too, isn't she?}Em ấy giận cũng dễ thương nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.56,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Er, uh, yes. She is—}À vâng. Chị ấy--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.64,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Please don't make him say that!}Đừng bắt em ấy nói nữa--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:18.64,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Now, now.... Since you're here, \NKatase-san, why don't you join us?}Thôi nào... Em cũng qua ngồi cùng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:20.15,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{O-Okay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.18,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Have to say, it's nostalgic to think about.}Chà, hoài niệm ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:26.89,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Do you remember when \NShinozaki-kun first joined up?}Em còn nhờ lần đầu Shinozaki đến công ty không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:30.16,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I mean, it wasn't really that long ago...}Chuyện đó lâu lắm rồi mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:33.63,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{I suppose you're right! \NIt was just a while back.}Phải nhỉ. Cứ như mới hôm qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:37.17,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are we still talking about this?! \NIt's ancient news!}Cơ mà vẫn còn nói mấy chuyện đó hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:42.06,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{My name is Shinozaki Takuma, \Nand I'll be working here starting today.}Tên tôi là Shinozaki Takuma, \Ntừ hôm nay sẽ làm việc ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.55,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's nice to meet all of you!}Rất mong được giúp đỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.82,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{I'm Akina, your manager.\NNice to meet you.}Tôi là Akina, quản lý. Rất vui được gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:49.29,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yes, sir! Thanks in advance for your guidance!}Vâng! Mong anh hướng dẫn ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:51.31,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's a pleasure to be working for you!}Rất vui được làm việc với anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.65,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{This is Katase-san.}Đây là Katase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:57.61,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{You'll be sitting next to her, \Nso if you have questions, she'll help you.}Em sẽ ngồi cạnh em ấy. Có gì không hiểu nhớ hỏi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:02.70,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm Katase. If you need to \Nknow anything, just ask.}Chị là Katase. Cần gì cứ hỏi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.57,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{So tiny! And cute!}Nhỏ xíu dễ thương quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.82,Flashback - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{A kohai! I got a kohai!}Đàn em! Đàn em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:08.46,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What is this fluttery, little creature?!}Thứ sinh vật dễ thương này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.80,Flashback - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{A kohai, a kohai!}Đàn em, đàn em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.58,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I can't believe my seat \Ngets such benefits...}Không thể tin mình lại được ngồi cạnh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.04,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{Someone's excited!}Có ai đó đang hứng thú kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.61,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Please, Manager, cut that out!}Thôi mà quản lý!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:18.08,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Heartwarming...}Ấm áp...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:21.71,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Let's start with getting your PC set up.}Đầu tiên thiết lập PC nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:22.84,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.47,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{This company seems great.}Công ty này có vẻ tuyệt vời.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:28.26,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I get a feeling this job will be fun.}Cảm giác công việc sẽ vui lắm đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:32.47,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She's staring a hole in me!}Bị nhìn chằm chằm kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:35.10,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's a gaze that won't let \Na single mistake slip by...}Ánh mắt sẽ xử ngay nếu mình làm sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.98,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{not of concern, but of oversight!}không phải quan tâm mà là giám sát...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.36,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Wait...}Khoan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.85,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Could that friendly act \Nfrom earlier be a facade}Không lẽ không khí thân thiện là giả,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:45.20,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{to get my to lower my guard \Nbefore they harshly evaluate me?!}để khiến mình mất cảnh giác và đưa ra đánh giá?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:46.49,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I dunno about this one.}Cũng không tệ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.74,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{You don't, eh?}Thế à...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.43,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{In that case, I better stay on my toes!}Nếu vậy thì phải cố gắng thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:53.85,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Maybe I can't make a good impression,\Nbut I can at least avoid a bad one!}Tuy không được điểm cộng nhưng phải tránh bị trừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:59.25,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Her gaze is getting even more intense!}Càng này càng ngột ngạt...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.00,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Ủa?
