Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.38,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs14\c&HFCFFFC&\bord2\shad0\pos(446,260.667)\3c&HD5D1BF&}{Cancel}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.98,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{A network password?}Mật khẩu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:07.98,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I don't think I mixed up the procedure...}Mình không nghĩ rằng nhầm lẫn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:10.91,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And I've got all the paperwork \NI was given here.}Và còn cả tài liệu hướng dẫn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:11.85,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Which leaves...}Tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:17.48,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I should probably ask about this, \Nbut what if I get the timing wrong?}Mình phải hỏi điều này, nhưng nhỡ sai thời điểm thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:19.13,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{If I'm too fast...}Nếu nhanh quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:22.98,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\fnComic Sans MS\b1\fscx120\fs30\c&H000000&\an5\bord0\shad0\pos(75,113)}{Too\Nfast}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.94,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are you really asking without \Nactually looking into the issue?}Chưa tìm hiểu gì đã hỏi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:28.74,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(375,0)\fnComic Sans MS\b1\fscx120\fs30\c&H000000&\an5\bord0\shad0\pos(75,113)}{Too\NSlow}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.59,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{If I take too long...}Nếu chậm quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:28.74,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Why didn't you ask sooner? You wasted time.}Sao không hỏi sớm hơn. Mất thời gian quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.36,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Which is it?!}Cái nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:33.56,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{For now, I should check the guidelines again...}Thôi, kiểm tra lại sách hướng dẫn đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:39.36,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{For the network password, it's your branch \Nname and then your employee ID number.}Với mạng nội bộ thì tài khoản \Nlà tên công ty, mật khẩu là số ID của em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.64,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Th-Thank you...}C-Cảm ơn chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:46.76,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{You were totally intimidated by \NKatase-san at first, weren't you?}Lúc đó em sợ Katase lắm nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:50.33,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's more like... I was getting nervous\Nand freaking out a bit.}Lúc đó... em cảm thấy lo lắng và sợ cùng lúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It was the same for me.}Chị cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:55.26,Flashback_Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Staaare...}Chằm chằm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.18,Flashback_Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san.}Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.17,Flashback_Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Is there anything you don't understand?}Có gì không hiểu không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:04.27,Flashback_Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You can ask me about it, y'know? \NI'm just waiting to be helpful!}Em có thể hỏi bất cứ gì. Chị đang chờ nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:05.40,Flashback_Italics,Manager,0,0,0,,{Glance.}Nhìn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.86,Flashback_Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But I can't! Manager will make fun \Nof me for making a fuss again...}Không được! Quản lý sẽ lại chọc mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:12.62,Flashback_Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Just stay focused and \Nkeep from grinning too much...}Phải tập trung và nhìn chằm chằm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.49,Flashback_Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{He seems to be having some trouble.}Có vẻ em ấy đang gặp rắc rối.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.02,Flashback_Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{This looks like a job for his senpai!}Đây là công việc của đàn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:23.11,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{For the network password, it's your branch \Nname and then your employee ID number.}Với mạng nội bộ thì tài khoản \Nlà tên công ty, mật khẩu là số ID của em.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.29,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Th-Thank you...}C-Cảm ơn chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.74,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, sorry, I shouldn't impose.}A, xin lỗi vì tự tiện...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.84,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{No, it's okay.\N I should've been the one to ask.}Không sao. Đáng ra em nên hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:36.10,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But really, if you have \Nquestions, don't hesitate.}Nhưng nếu không hiểu gì phải hỏi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.08,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sure!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:40.25,Flashback_Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She really was worried...}Chị ấy đã rất lo lắng cho mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:43.65,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Thanks for your concern, Senpai.}Cảm ơn vì đã quan tâm đến em.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:50.69,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, should I not call you Senpai? Is it \Nunprofessional? Too much like a student?}A, em không nên gọi như kiểu sinh viên nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:56.58,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\b1\fscx120\fs22\c&H000000&\an5\bord0\shad0\pos(75,295)}{Kohai\NCuteness\NMeter}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:57.53,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai?}Chị ơi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:58.65,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yes!}Sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:07:59.36,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai?}Chị à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:00.52,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yes, right!}Gì em?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:01.24,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai...?}Chị...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:02.58,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yes, that's me, your senpai!}Đúng đó, là đàn chị đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.09,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, sorry... it's just...}Xin lỗi... chỉ là...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.79,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm really excited \Nabout having my first kohai....}Chị thấy vui khi có đàn em...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:12.89,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{And I've been trying to stay calm, but...}Và nãy giờ đang cố gắng bình tĩnh nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:16.60,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I guess I haven't been \Nconducting myself like a senpai.}Lại để em thấy một đàn chị đáng xấu hổ rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:19.93,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{No! I'm glad if you're glad!}Không không! Em rất vui mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:24.12,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I was also excited about \Nmeeting my first work senpai, so...}Em cũng thấy háo hức\N khi có đàn chị đầu tiên trong công ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:29.32,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I guess this is a first for both of us, huh?}Có lẽ đây là lần đầu của hai ta nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:33.20,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Well, since we're both new at this, \Nlet's try our best!}Vì chưa có kinh nghiệm nên hãy cùng cố hết sức nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.20,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{R-Right!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.69,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{Did I just pick up some lewd vibes...?}Ngửi thấy mùi mờ ám...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:41.21,Flashback,Shiori/Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You did not!}Không có!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.22,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Ah, that really takes me back!}Chà, hoài niệm ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:44.96,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:46.83,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{What's wrong, you two?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.04,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's kind of embarrassing to think about...}Hơi xấu hổ khi nghĩ lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:50.96,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Agreed.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.20,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{I see.}Thế à.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:54.97,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Well, to make up for embarrassing you two...}Vì đã khiến hai em xấu hổ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.47,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Dessert will be my treat. What would you like?}Tôi sẽ đãi tráng miệng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:02.22,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Really?! Thank you so much!}Thật sao? Cảm ơn anh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What should I get...?}Chọn món gì đây nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:07.23,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai, you let him buy you off \Na little too easily.}Chị dễ bị dụ quá đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Do you not want dessert, Shinozaki-san?}Em không muốn ăn hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.62,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{If you don't, I'd be glad to eat yours!}Nếu không thì để chị ăn cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.76,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'll take mine, thanks!}Không, em ăn chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:15.99,Main,Manager,0,0,0,,{Oh, dear.}Chà chà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:19.63,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are you ready for tomorrow's meeting?}Đã sẵn sàng cho buổi họp ngày mai chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:20.56,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{All set!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.61,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Very good!}Tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:26.34,Main,Eyecatch/Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My Tiny Senpai}{\i0}{.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Good work today!}Em vất vả rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:34.26,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I got super nervous having a \Nmeeting at another company...}Em lo lắng khi đi gặp đối tác lắm đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:36.54,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You do, don't you?}Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:40.57,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It was a huge relief having you backing me up.}Có chị ở đó làm em yên tâm hơn hẳn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:46.80,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Was it a good reminder that I'm your senpai?}Thầm cảm ơn vì chị là đàn chị của em hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.31,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It was!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:52.89,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Well, let's head back to the office \Nand get back to work!}Thôi, về công ty làm việc nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.15,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{R-Right!}V-Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{So cute!}Dễ thương quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.96,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Is it some kind of mascot character?}Linh vật hay gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:15.21,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{A kitty with a bunny hoodie, \Nand a doggy with a bear hoodie!}Mèo mặc hoodie thỏ và chó mặt hoodie gấu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:19.09,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Y'know, this stuffed animal...}Đám thú nhồi bông này...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:21.95,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Something about this stuffed animal...}Đám thú nhồi bông này...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.92,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It reminds me of Senpai.}Làm mình nhớ đến chị ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.92,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It reminds me of Shinozaki-san.}Làm mình nhớ đến Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Nhớ đến...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:32.19,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Is this how I look to you?}Chị trông giống thế trong mắt em à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:35.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Well, when I say that, I mean...}À thì... ý em là...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:42.62,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You can say "You're that cute!" \NIt's the perfect time to say it, me!}Đây là lúc phải nói "Chị dễ thương y như vậy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:46.37,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Y-You are kinda catlike, I'd say...}E-Em nghĩ chị giống con mèo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You really think so?}Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:50.75,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Extremely feline!}Y chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:54.38,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And is this how you see me, Senpai?}Và kia là em trong mắt chị à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{There's something about his gaze,}Cái ánh mắt đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:00.80,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{and the unique look\Nof a dog in a bear hoodie...}và vẻ ngoài độc đáo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.55,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I dare say he's 90% Shinozaki-san.}99% giống như em.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:05.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Almost 100%?!}Gần 100%?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:12.59,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Well... would you like me to catch them?}À... để em gắp cho chị nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:14.81,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Can you?!}Được hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:15.65,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I think so.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:19.47,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{When I was in high school, \NI used to spend a lot of time at the arcade,}Hồi còn học cấp 3, em hay đến đây chơi lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:23.59,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{and I had a pretty decent collection \Nof cute plushies like these.}Và có cả một bộ sưu tập thú bông luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:27.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You must like cute things, Shinozaki-san.}Em hẳn thích những thứ dễ thương lắm nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.10,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I do.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.40,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{One of the reasons I applied to Sunpick was}Lý do em vào Sunpick làm
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:34.50,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{because I wanted to be involved in \Nmaking that sort of thing.}vì em muốn tạo ra một thứ dễ thương.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I like that.}Chị thích lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:39.92,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Cute things, I mean!}Những thứ dễ thương.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:44.77,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I see! That makes sense... \NGot kind of worked up there.}Cái đó à... tí thì hiểu lầm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.04,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Is something wrong?}Có gì hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.22,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, no, nothing.}À không ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:52.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Our company's character, Meowtaro, \Nis cute, too, isn't he?}Linh vật công ty ta dễ thương nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:56.75,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{We had plenty of Meowtaro \Nmerch at home, too.}Chúng ta cũng có nhiều sản phẩm ăn theo nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:58.86,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{My sister is six years older, \Nand she loves him.}Chị em lớn hơn em 6 tuổi mà còn thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:04.11,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Me liking cute stuff might be \Nher influence, come to think of it.}Với cả em cũng bị ảnh hưởng từ chị ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:08.62,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{So you're a big sister's boy, Shinozaki-san?}Vậy là em thích chị mình lắm nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.83,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I dunno if I'd say that.}Em cũng không biết nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.78,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's cute.}Dễ thương ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:21.38,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Y-You're the cute one, Senpai!}C-Chị cũng thế đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.78,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Okay, here we go.}Rồi, em gắp đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:27.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Okay. Good luck!}Ừm, cố lên nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:33.64,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, boy! Oh, boy! Oh, boy! Oh, boy...}Ôi ôi ôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:37.65,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sulk...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:39.79,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That was a close one.}Xém nữa thì.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:42.15,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I got more than \Na 100 yen's worth of value, for sure.}Mình bỏ 100 yên và thu lại món quà vô giá!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:44.82,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I get the feeling I can manage on the next one.}Lần tới em có thể thành công.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.68,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are you sure?}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:48.99,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I want to protect this smile.}Mình muốn bảo vệ nụ cười đó.
