Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:55.53,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, boy! Oh, boy! Oh, boy! Oh, boy...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:02.24,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Almost got 'em.}Xém nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:04.26,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I could watch this all day.}Mình có thể nhìn cảnh này cả ngày...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:07.26,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sorry about that, Senpai. But this time...}Xin lỗi chị, nhưng lần tới...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:10.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about it, Shinozaki-san.}Đừng lo Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.89,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Even if you don't manage on the next one...}Dù lần tới không được...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:14.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{My budget is 30,000!}Thì chị còn hẳn 30.000 yên lận.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:17.15,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{The height of a child with \Nthe purchasing power of an adult!}Chị dùng sức mạnh người lớn vào trò chơi trẻ con à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.90,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Is this gonna work...?}Có thể được...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Do you think...?}Chắc thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.32,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's caught on the bear.}Nó kéo theo con gấu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:29.95,Italics,Chicken,0,0,0,,{Buck...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.18,Italics,Chicken,0,0,0,,{Buck-kaw!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.13,Main,Shiori/Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{All right!}Tuyệt quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:39.93,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry...}X-xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:41.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's fine.}K-Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:44.01,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Two at once! Nicely done!}Được cả 2 luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:47.26,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Nah, that was a coincidence.}Chắc là trùng hợp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:53.01,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Maybe the other one was worried \Nabout being lonely and tagged along.}Có lẽ em thấy cô đơn khi bạn mình biến mất nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:55.42,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Th-That might be it.}C-Có thể là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:58.27,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And you said that one reminded you of me...}Và chị ấy nói nó giống mình tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:03.78,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{In that case, they should \Nstay together, so they don't get lonely.}Vậy thì cả hai sẽ ở cạnh nhau \Nđể không cô đơn nữa nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.78,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Together...!}Cùng nhau!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:13.16,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She means the stuffed animals! That's all!}Ý chị ấy là thú nhồi bông!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:16.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Now that we've got them, let's name them!}Giờ thì đặt tên thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:20.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Since this one's a bear dog \Nthat looks like Shinozaki-san...}Bé này là gấu chó mà giống Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:21.98,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Takuma-kun!}Takuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:23.79,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Nghe cũng được đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:28.68,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(446,30)\an8\fs14\fnComic Sans MS\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0\b1}{Shinozaki           Ta}{\c&H1201CB&}{kuma}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:26.78,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Is that bad? \NI like how it has "kuma" like bear.}Không ổn hả? Chị lấy đuôi của tên em ghép vào đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.68,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I didn't say no!}Không hẳn là không...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:30.92,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{In that case, this one...}Vậy thì con này...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:33.68,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Should probably be "Shiori-san," right?}Sẽ là Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That's fine by me.}Cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.68,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It is?!}Thế á?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:41.34,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{They'd get along as senpai and kohai, then.}Và chúng sẽ là đàn em và đàn chị thân thiết.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:43.06,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{G-Good point...}V-vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:46.35,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Something about this is giving me \Nbutterflies in my tummy...}Cái cảm giác phấn khởi này là sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:47.69,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san.}Shinozaki nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:52.32,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Thank you for getting \Nthese stuffed animals for me.}Cảm ơn vì đã lấy nó cho chị nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:56.58,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Were you really that glad about it?}Chị vui đến thế ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:58.01,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:05.17,Flashback,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{This one should probably be \N"Shiori-san", right?}Con này phải là Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:11.40,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Okay, let's head back to the office!}Thôi, về công ty nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:12.22,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Right!}Vâng!
