Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.22,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san, Shinozaki-kun...}Hayakawa, Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.19,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Could you come here for a sec?}Có rảnh không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:24.44,Sign_Basic,BG Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(332,36)\an8\fnTimes New Roman\c&H92D5E5&\bord0\b1\4c&H456070&\shad2}{40th Anniversary}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:24.44,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{A Meowtaro video game?}Video game Nyantaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:30.26,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Yep. I volunteered to design it, \Nand I wanted to get some opinions.}Phải, tôi tình nguyện thiết kế nó nên\N cần tham khảo ý kiến 2 người.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:32.11,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{What kind of game is it?}Thể loại game gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:34.58,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{A dating sim.}Game hẹn hò.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.99,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{It's an otome game!}Otome game đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.02,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{A Meowtaro...}Nyantaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:42.75,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Otome game?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:46.75,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{I've got a start menu ready, so take a look}Tôi đã hoàn thành màn hình bắt đầu nè, xem đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:47.82,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{See?}Đây.
