Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:54.47,Sign_Basic,Start Menu Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H26828C&\3c&H79D2E7&\shad0\fs16\pos(354.667,257.334)}{Start}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.93,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Wh-What the...?}C-Cái gì--?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.47,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Say hello to the anthropomorphized \Nhot version of Meowtaro!}Phiên bản nhân hoá của Nyantaro đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:58.35,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{The idea is to seize control of \Nthe latent otome game fan demographic!}Chúng ta sẽ chiếm lấy những người chơi dòng otome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.03,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Would that work?}Có thành công không đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:01.76,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I guess it could.}Chắc là có thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.10,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I see...}Hiểu rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:06.35,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm not sure what fans of \Nclassic Meowtaro will think of this, though.}Nhưng mà người hâm mộ cũ sẽ nghĩ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:09.24,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I thought you all had gone home. \NWhat are you doing?}Mọi người không về mà làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.28,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Speaking of classic fans!}Người hâm mộ cũ kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:16.25,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Katase-san, I'd love to hear your opinion.}Em cũng muốn nghe ý kiến của chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.78,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Check out the Meowtaro video game!}Về game cho Nyantaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:20.41,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{A Meowtaro video game?!}Game cho Nyantaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.79,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Here it is!}Đây ạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.64,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{What do you think, Katase-san?}Chị thấy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:28.55,Main,Yamagishi (F),0,0,0,,{It's an otome game featuring \Nan anthropomorphized hot version of Meowtaro!}Là otome game nhân hoá Nyantaro đẹp trai đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.12,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{This is Meowtaro...?}Đây là Nyantaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:30.86,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Hot?}Đẹp trai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:31.74,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Anthropomorphized?}Nhân hoá?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:33.04,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{And this is Meowtaro...}Và đây là Nyantaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:34.30,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What in the world...?}Thế giới này là sao...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:39.31,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai's neural circuits have shorted out!}Não chị ấy quá tải rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:44.31,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Now, what I really wanted to ask you about \Nare some romantic anecdotes.}Giờ thì tôi muốn hỏi về mấy chuyện yêu đương.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:46.44,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Romantic anecdotes?}Chuyện yêu đương?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:51.37,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Remember, this is a Meowtaro dating sim.}Tôi nói game này là về hẹn hò rồi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:56.20,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{So I was hoping to hear about all kinds of \Nromantic stories, for reference!}Nên cần phải tham khảo mấy chuyện tình lãng mạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:59.62,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{R-Romantic anecdotes, huh...?}C-Chuyện yêu đương à...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.41,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fntimes new roman\b1\fscx120\fs22\c&H000000&\an6\bord0\shad0\fsp4\pos(337.084,169.8)}{Never had a\Nboyfriend}Chưa từng có bạn trai
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:03.34,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Th-This is kind of sudden...}T-Tự nhiên lại bảo thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:04.21,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fntimes new roman\b1\fscx120\fs22\c&H000000&\an6\bord0\shad0\fsp4\pos(337.084,169.8)}{Never had a\Nboyfriend}Chưa từng có bạn gái
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:08.33,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah. It's hard to \Nthink of anything that'd help...}P-Phải đó! Chuyện này có hơi khó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:08.33,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fntimes new roman\b1\fscx120\fs22\c&H000000&\an6\bord0\shad0\fsp4\pos(337.084,169.8)}{Never had a\Nboyfriend}Chưa từng có bạn trai
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:11.84,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(408,82)\an8\fntimes new roman\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0\b1}{Total Romantic Experience: Zero}Kinh nghiệm:0
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.53,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Wait, have none of you been \Nin a relationship before?}Ba người không có kinh nghiệm yêu đương à?
