Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:16.84,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{C-Come to think of it, Hayakawa, \Nwhen you were interviewing for Sunpick,}C-Cơ mà Hayakawa, hồi phỏng vấn Sunpick,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.88,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{didn't you say you ran into Prince Charming?}cậu nói đã đụng phải Hoàng tử quyến rũ gì mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:22.47,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{You wanna talk about that }{\i1}{now}{\i0}{?!}Hả? Giờ này nói về chuyện đó á?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:25.34,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{What is that all about?! Spill the details!}Gì thế? Mau nói đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.86,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Well... it wasn't that big of a deal.}Chuyện cũng không có gì.
