Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:40.12,Flashback_Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I can't believe this happened \Nright before an important interview...}Không thể tin lại xảy ra ngay trước buổi phỏng vấn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:42.12,Flashback_Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I really screwed up...}Chết tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:43.82,Flashback_Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{What now?}Sao giờ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:45.66,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{Are you all right?}Em ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.25,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{You've got an interview, right?}Em chuẩn bị phỏng vấn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.04,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes...}V-Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:53.78,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{One second.}Chờ tí nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.29,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{There you go.}Vậy là ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:59.26,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much.}Cảm ơn anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:02.49,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{It'll be a while \Nuntil it dries completely, but...}Chờ chút nữa nó sẽ khô lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:03.60,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Try it on.}Em mang vào đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:06.60,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{O-Okay.}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:14.71,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{Good luck with the interview.}Phỏng vấn cố lên nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.11,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{R-Right...}V-Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:20.89,Flashback,Manager,0,0,0,,{Be seeing you.}Vậy thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.55,Flashback_Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Does he work at Sunpick...?}Anh ấy làm việc ở Sunpick à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.76,Flashback,Office Worker (30s; female),0,0,0,,{Could the next interviewee please come in?}Mời người tiếp theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:32.63,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Coming!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:36.25,Flashback_Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I wonder if I'll see him again \Nif I get the job...}Mình sẽ gặp lại nếu đậu phỏng vấn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.68,Flashback_Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{No, not now!}Không không phải lúc!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.76,Flashback_Italics,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I need to focus on the interview!}Phải tập trung phỏng vấn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:43.26,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Pardon me.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:49.70,Flashback,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{My name is Hayakawa Chinatsu. \NThank you for your time today.}Tôi tên là Hayakawa Chinatsu, rất mong được giúp đỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:58.36,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{So the person who helped you was one of \Nthe people conducting the interview?}Vậy người giúp đỡ em lại là người phỏng vấn luôn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:01.63,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That feels an awful lot like fate!}Cứ như định mệnh vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:04.96,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Who was it, anyway? Did you \Nsee him again after getting the job?}Cơ mà đó là ai? Sau khi vào công ty có gặp lại không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.87,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{W-Well, I did, but...}C-Có ạ... nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.14,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{The thing about fireworks is...}Pháo hoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:16.75,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{they're pretty because \Nyou see them at a distance.}chỉ đẹp khi ngắm từ xa nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:19.26,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{She got weirdly philosophical about it!}Sao tự nhiên triết lý vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:24.28,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Never mind that! I told one, \Nso you need to, too, Yamagishi-san!}Bỏ đi! Tôi nói rồi thì Yamagishi cũng nói gì đi chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.01,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{Me?! I...}Tôi á?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:30.89,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{I mean, obviously I don't have any! \NThat's the whole reason I'm asking!}Tôi... làm gì có! Không có mới hỏi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.77,Main,Yamagishi(F),0,0,0,,{The way you believe me is kind of depressing...}Nên là cũng như mọi người...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:38.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Romantic anecdotes...}Chuyện tình yêu à...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:48.96,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Since this one's a bear dog \Nthat looks like Shinozaki-san...}Con gấu chó này giống Shinozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.16,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Takuma-kun!}Takuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:55.12,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I can't believe I said that, much less \Nthat I'm thinking about it now.}Mình đã vô thức nói thế không suy nghĩ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:58.55,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm so embarrassed about \Nwhat I said, in hindsight.}Giờ nghĩ lại xấu hổ thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:04.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Still, it's just a stuffed animal. It has \Nnothing to do with the real Shinozaki-san.}Cơ mà chỉ là thú bông thôi, \Nkhông liên quan gì em ấy cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.81,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Hình như trong ngăn kéo có...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:11.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Ta-da!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:13.44,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I added a necktie.}Mình đã thêm cà vạt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Pretty good if I say so myself.}Giờ thì quá tuyệt vời.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:19.15,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Why am I making the resemblance even stronger?!}Tại sao mình lại làm thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.39,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Bình tĩnh lại nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.65,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's just a stuffed animal.}Chỉ là thú bông thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:24.66,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Just a stuffed...}Đó chỉ là...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:35.67,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Stuffed animal! It's just a stuffed animal!}Thú bông! Chỉ là thú bông!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:52.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Maybe I should rearrange them \Nso he's out of sight...}Phải sắp xếp lại để khuất tầm nhìn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:57.85,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shiori-san's on top of Takuma-kun!}Shiori đang nằm trên Takuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:02.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Shiori-san...}Chị Shiori...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:05.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Takuma-kun...}Takuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.95,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shiori-san! You can't!}Không được Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:28.26,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shiori-san and Takuma-kun.}Shiori và Takuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:32.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{A senpai and a kohai who get along!}Đàn em và đàn chị thân thiết.
